{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"","closed_at":null,"closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"15ba7b153838c008a30ade54cf5a1aef5b467e4be1f3ca6352034911a66d6ebe","created_at":"2026-03-03T22:23:30Z","created_by":"saurabhav88","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"Implement tiered paste system to replace single-method CGEvent Cmd+V approach. Validated by Gemini + OpenAI.\n\nARCHITECTURE (ordered cascade):\n- Tier 1: AX direct insertion via kAXSelectedTextAttribute on captured AXFocusedUIElement (zero disruption, no clipboard, no focus change)\n- Tier 2: Activate app + CGEvent Cmd+V via .cgAnnotatedSessionEventTap (current approach, refined with AXObserver-based paste confirmation)\n- Tier 2b: AppleScript Edit \u003e Paste (sandboxed app fallback, requires frontmost)  \n- Tier 3: Clipboard + user notification (graceful failure, text never lost)\n\nKEY IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS:\n- Capture AXFocusedUIElement at PTT start (alongside existing NSRunningApplication)\n- All AX calls on MainActor (AXUIElement is Sendable but operations are not thread-safe)\n- Set AXTimeout(1.0s) before AX writes to avoid 30s hang on misbehaving apps\n- Verify kAXRoleAttribute == textField/textArea before Tier 1 attempt\n- Log (bundle_id, successful_tier, duration_ms) for compatibility analytics\n- Switch CGEvent tap from .cghidEventTap to .cgAnnotatedSessionEventTap\n\nFILES TO MODIFY:\n1. TranscriptionPipeline.swift — add targetElement capture + tiered paste cascade\n2. PasteService.swift — add insertViaAccessibility(), pasteViaAppleScript(), switch event tap, add AXObserver paste confirmation\n3. Constants.swift — paste confirmation polling constants\n\nSOURCES: Hex (kitlangton/Hex), speak2 (zachswift615/speak2), Gemini, OpenAI","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"ew-zwn","is_template":0,"issue_type":"feature","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"saurabhav@gmail.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":2,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"in_progress","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"Implement tiered paste system (AX direct → CGEvent → AppleScript → clipboard)","updated_at":"2026-03-03T23:01:35Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
